msgctxt "#33048"
msgid "Use the Emby path substitution to format your path correctly or ensure your path is added to Kodi's file manager. For more information, check the FAQ in Emby for Kodi's github wiki. Stop syncing?"
msgstr "配置 Emby 路径替换功能，或确保将路径添加到 Kodi 文件管理器。 有关更多信息，请查看 Emby for Kodi 官方 github wiki 中的常见问题解答。是否停止同步？"

