msgctxt "#33301"
msgid "Compatibility mode changes the plugin id to 4.x (plugin.video.emby). Don't use it if it's not absolutly required! Never perform updates in this mode!"
msgstr "兼容模式会将插件 ID 更改为 4.x 版本（plugin.video.emby）。除非绝对必要，请勿使用此模式！在此模式下严禁进行任何插件更新！"

msgctxt "#33302"
msgid "In some circumstances (WLan, delayed network startup etc.) a delayed plugin start can improve connectivity"
msgstr "在某些情况下（如使用无线网络、网络启动延迟等），延迟启动插件可以提高连接稳定性。"

msgctxt "#33303"
msgid "You can adjust what meta information are loaded for dynamic (not synced) content. By default only basic information are loaded. Extenting can delay browsing lists."
msgstr "您可以调整动态内容（未同步内容）的元数据加载项。默认情况下仅加载基础元数据。扩展加载项可能会导致列表浏览出现延迟。"

msgctxt "#33304"
msgid "Be careful with this option. It offers FILE DELETE not only database removal. (Admin permissions are required)"
msgstr "请谨慎使用此选项。它执行的是物理文件删除操作，而非仅移除数据库记录。（需管理员权限）"

msgctxt "#33305"
msgid "This is a debug option. You can set the last sync date/time manually. After Kodi restart it will perform the action. Just perform minor adjustments. Setting a date/time too much in the past can cause a huge incremental sync."
msgstr "这是一个调试选项。您可以手动设置“最后同步日期/时间”。Kodi 重启后将执行该操作。请仅进行微调。将日期/时间设置得过早会导致极其庞大的增量同步。"

msgctxt "#33306"
msgid "Resets the unique device id. A manual reconnection to emby server is required. Otherwise the realtime communication could be compromised."
msgstr "重置唯一设备 ID。操作后需要手动重新连接 Emby 服务器。否则，实时通信功能可能会受到影响。"

msgctxt "#33307"
msgid "Connect to a new Emby server (multiserver) or reconnect an existing Emby server (debug)"
msgstr "连接到新的 Emby 服务器（多服务器模式）或重新连接现有的 Emby 服务器（调试模式）"

msgctxt "#33308"
msgid "Show hidden users on Emby server for connections ops."
msgstr "在执行连接操作时，显示 Emby 服务器上的隐藏用户。"

msgctxt "#33309"
msgid "Add/Remove/Repair libraries, live TV, themes."
msgstr "添加/删除/修复媒体库、直播电视、主题。"

msgctxt "#33310"
msgid "Syncs all artwork locally to Kodi. This can take very long. Kodi's webserver must be enabled, but not in SSL mode (not supported yet). Caching can not be interrupted beside restarting Kodi."
msgstr "将所有艺术图同步并缓存到 Kodi 本地。这可能耗时极长。必须启用 Kodi 的 Web 服务器，且不能处于 SSL 模式（目前尚不支持）。除了重启 Kodi 外，缓存过程无法中断。"

msgctxt "#33311"
msgid "Some skins use xps playlists. Usually not required, leave it off if you don't need them."
msgstr "某些皮肤会使用 xps 播放列表。该功能通常并不需要此功能，如您不需要，请保持关闭状态。"

msgctxt "#33312"
msgid "Userrating are additional information to be synced to Kodi. In some minor cases (3rd party plugins like trakt etc.) can interfere with synced userratings. Default should be on. If you change this setting, a full database resync is mandatory to apply the change."
msgstr "“用户评分”是同步到 Kodi 的额外信息。在极少数情况下（如使用 Trakt 等第三方插件），可能会与同步的评分产生冲突。默认建议开启。如果您更改此设置，必须进行“全量数据库同步”才能生效。"

msgctxt "#33313"
msgid "Performs a complete Kodi database resync. Settings and artwork are optionally reset."
msgstr "执行完整的 Kodi 数据库重新同步。设置项和艺术图（海报等）可选择性重置。"

msgctxt "#33314"
msgid "Cinema mode is a premiere feature of Emby. Trailer configurations are support on Emby server (number of trailers to be played etc.)"
msgstr "影院模式是 Emby 的首映（会员）功能。您可以在 Emby 服务器端配置预告片的详细参数（例如播放预告片的数量等）。"

msgctxt "#33315"
msgid "Transcode audio bitrate"
msgstr "转码音频比特率"

msgctxt "#33316"
msgid "Network speed. Bitrates which exceeds the bandwidth will be transcoded."
msgstr "网络速度设置。超过此带宽限制的视频码率将被强制转码。"

msgctxt "#33318"
msgid "Devicename report to Emby server."
msgstr "上报至 Emby 服务器的设备名称。"

msgctxt "#33319"
msgid "Report playback progress to additional users."
msgstr "向其他用户报告播放进度。"

msgctxt "#33320"
msgid "Gap between playback stopped and continuation start."
msgstr "播放停止与继续播放起始点之间的间隔（缓冲时长）。"

